data.title: SNSA - SonicWall Network Security Administrator
data.meta_description: This course will provide skills to successfully designi, implement, and troubleshoot SonicWall firewall appliances and security services. Exam voucher provided.
data.text:
The SonicWall Network Security Administrator (SNSA) for SonicOS 7.0curriculum provides students the required background, knowledge, and hands-on experience to begin designing, implementing, and troubleshooting SonicWall Network Security products. SonicOS 7 is SonicWallâ€™s brand new and most advanced security operating system and is at the core of its latest physical and virtual firewalls, including models from the TZ, NSv, NSa and NSsp Series. SonicOS 7.0 features advanced security, simplified policy management, and critical networking and management capabilities for distributed enterprises and small- to medium-sized businesses with SD-branch support.

Be advised that with the purchase of this class you will receive ONE FREE EXAM VOUCHER in order to help you pass the SNSA certification.
